---
import Layout from "@/layouts/BlogLayout.astro";
const obj = {
  title: "Privacy Policy | Github Boost",
};
---

<Layout postDetails={obj}>
  <main class="py-10">
    <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>
      Thank you for using the PR Review Helper Chrome Extension. Your privacy is
      important to us. This privacy policy explains what information we collect,
      how we use it, and your rights regarding your data.
    </p>

    <h5>Information We Collect</h5>
    <p>
      We do not collect, store, process, or share any personal information or
      data from users. The PR Review Helper extension operates entirely on your
      local machine and does not transmit any data to external servers.
    </p>

    <h5>How We Use Information</h5>
    <p>
      Since we do not collect any user data, there is no information for us to
      use, process, or share. All operations are performed locally within your
      browser environment.
    </p>

    <h5>Third-Party Services</h5>
    <p>
      This extension does not use any third-party services that could
      potentially access your data.
    </p>

    <h5>Changes to This Policy</h5>
    <p>
      We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be
      posted on this page. We encourage you to review this policy periodically
      to stay informed about how we protect your privacy.
    </p>

    <h5>Contact Us</h5>
    <p>
      If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please
      contact us at contact@mdsaban.com.
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>
